.container
  .row
    .confidence
      .span4
        .badge.compliance
        %h2.green compliance
        %p  We are a full service pharmacy that fills all of your medications in one roll of simple, sealed, easy-to-use packets, that are packaged by date and time of administration rather than by medication.
      .span4
        .badge.convenience
        %h2.red convenience
        %p All medications are delivered together at the same time every month, saving you the time and headaches associated with multiple monthly trips to the pharmacy.
      .span4
        .badge.continuity
        %h2.blue continuity of care
        %p Keep your physician in the loop with our prescriber dashboard, which allows your doctor to monitor your current medication therapy.
 
